------------------------------------ |\n    83\t| `target_id` | `string` | 是   
| 目标用户 ID                              |\n    84\t| `action`    | `string` |
是   | 操作类型：`like` / `pass` / `super_like` |\n    85\t\n    86\t#### Respon
se 200 OK\n    87\t\n    88\t```json\n    89\t{\n    90\t  "data": {\n    91\t  
