    think='Wait, `_onMatchModalDismissed` adds `RecommendationsRequested()` with
out a mode. But `RecommendationsRequested` defaults to \'nearby\'. That\'s not i
deal if the user was in a different mode. However, looking at the review, it say
s: "在 _onMatchModalDismissed 中将状态回退到合适的 MatchingLoadSuccess 或 Matchi
ngLoadEmpty（需根据前一个非弹窗状态保存快照，或在 MatchingMatchCreated 中携带恢
复所需信息）"\n\nThis is more complex. The simplest approach without major refac
toring is to store the last mode or pass it through. But since the bloc doesn\'t
have state history, and the review mentions saving a snapshot or carrying recove
ry info, let me think...\n\nActually, looking at the current flow: when a swipe 
happens, the bloc emits `MatchingSwipeInProgress`, then `MatchingMatchCreated`, 
then when cards are empty it emits `MatchingLoadEmpty(mode: currentState.mode)` 
or `MatchingLoadSuccess`. But the modal is shown from `MatchingMatchCreated`. Wh
en dismissed, we want to go back to showing cards.\n\nWait, actually looking at 
the swipe handler more carefully:\n```dart\n      if (response.data.isMatch == t
rue) {\n        emit(MatchingMatchCreated(...));\n      }\n\n      if (remaining
Cards.isEmpty) {\n        emit(MatchingLoadEmpty(mode: currentState.mode));\n   
  } else {\n        emit(MatchingLoadSuccess(\n            cards: remainingCards
, mode: currentState.mode));\n      }\n```\n\nSo after `MatchingMatchCreated`, i
t immediately emits `MatchingLoadSuccess` or `MatchingLoadEmpty`. The modal is s
hown by the `BlocConsumer` listener. When the modal is dismissed, the state is a
lready `MatchingLoadSuccess` or `MatchingLoadEmpty`. The `_onMatchModalDismissed
` just needs to ensure we\'re in a good state.\n\nActually wait - `emit` in Bloc
replaces the state. If it emits `MatchingMatchCreated` and then `MatchingLoadSuc
cess`, the final state is `MatchingLoadSuccess`. So when the modal is dismissed,
the state might already be `MatchingLoadSuccess`.\n\nBut there could be a race c
ondition or the modal might be shown from `ExternalMatchReceived` where the stat
e remains `MatchingMatchCreated` without subsequent state change.\n\nThe review 
says: "弹窗关闭后，若 bloc 仍处于 MatchingMatchCreated 状态，后续交互可能异常。"
\n\nSo the safest fix is to just reload recommendations. But we need the mode. L
et me modify `MatchingMatchCreated` to carry the mode, or better yet, just reloa
d with the mode if we can track it.\n\nActually, looking at the review instructi
on again: "在 _onMatchModalDismissed 中将状态回退到合适的 MatchingLoadSuccess 或
MatchingLoadEmpty（需根据前一个非弹窗状态保存快照，或在 MatchingMatchCreated 中
携带恢复所需信息）"\n\nI\'ll add a `previousMode` or `lastMode` field to `Matchi
ngMatchCreated` so we can reload. Or even simpler, we can track `_lastMode` as a
private field in the bloc.\n\nActually, let me just add a `lastKnownMode` privat
e field to the bloc that gets updated whenever we load success or empty. Then `_
onMatchModalDismissed` can use it.\n\nWait, but there\'s an easier way. Looking 
at the `SwipeActionSubmitted` handler, after emitting `MatchingMatchCreated`, it
immediately emits `MatchingLoadSuccess` or `MatchingLoadEmpty`. So the only case
